# Workspace-root .dockerignore — applies to ALL image builds, since every
# Dockerfile in this monorepo is built with the repo ROOT as the build context
# (`docker build -f <pkg>/Dockerfile .`). Keeps the context small and prevents
# host build artifacts / secrets from leaking into the image.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/out
**/build
.git
.github
**/.github
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/coverage
# Stale per-repo npm lockfiles left over from the pre-monorepo split. The
# pnpm workspace uses the root pnpm-lock.yaml only; these must never be copied
# into a build (they would confuse npm/pnpm if present).
**/package-lock.json
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/npm-debug.log*
**/.DS_Store
**/README.md
**/docs
**/reference
# Desktop app + static site are not containerized here.
apps/forge-desktop
apps/site
